heading: Collapsed Vault Dungeon Guide
content: Collapsed Vault is a dungeon in northern Kehjistan that rewards you with the , a highly useful Druid aspect for group play. However, we can't recommend this dungeon as a farming destination. On top of the "Slay all enemies" objective in the first zone, the second zone is enormous and requires extensive backtracking to recover the Ancient Statues. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
